      'Established end-to-end pipelines to package and deploy the application as a production web app.',
    ],
    tech: ['Python', 'TensorFlow', 'RNN', 'Flask', 'Medical Imaging', 'Signal Processing'],
  },
  {
    company: 'Revature, LLC',
    role: 'Data Analyst Intern',
    location: 'Reston, VA',
    period: '09/2022 – 01/2023',
    current: false,
    highlights: [
      'Created notebooks for ensuring data warehouse integrity and quality checks in Azure Databricks.',
      'Developed visual reports and dashboards using Power BI; gained expertise in data warehouse ETL pipeline design.',
    ],
    tech: ['Azure Databricks', 'Power BI', 'Python', 'SQL', 'ETL', 'Data Warehousing'],
  },
  {
    company: 'The University of Texas at Arlington',
    role: 'Graduate Research Assistant',
